{"tid":406610,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[人如果無夢想..]如TVB用一億請周星馳返來還劇債你估佢肯唔肯？","createTime":"2017-09-19T19:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T04:40:13.000Z","uid":16697,"like":1,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"661f05d8f562c7f4162521d5856a3b12d10ff470","tid":406610,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T19:16:27.000Z","msg":"以本人所知周星馳好似仲有約<br />\n<br />\n周星馳當年係雜誌講過,想返TVB做幾日兒童節目主持,報答TVB知遇之恩<br />\n<br />\n二十年過後,已經神級地位既佢<br />\n<br />\n一億拍一套電視劇<br />\n全部所有野佢話事，包括簡演員<br />\n<br />\n星爺會唔會心動？<br />\n<br />\n好想見到星爺同朱千雪合作拍戲,之後再起電影捧起千雪<br />\n<br />\n星爺整返黑個頭,保養返d皮膚,起碼可以去返功夫果陣咁型<br />\n<br />\n星爺回歸,香港大陸網上收看點擊破百億唔出奇,呢個投資唸得過<br />\n<br />\nTVB高層,唸唸佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b524cfe01fe4e1c235e17e153eaaa197a4668064","tid":406610,"uid":550,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T19:18:06.000Z","msg":"你要星爺上Think Big教班細路英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe009fa6d6bc942ef8b5a89de6671e8c4dfd4ae6","tid":406610,"uid":56401,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T19:34:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 星爺是但拎自己個名返大陸拍套垃圾都幾億 你仲on99想搵佢拍劇<br />\n不了"},{"pid":"e837d417fca7055fd6cc23ca49b93e0ac3579506","tid":406610,"uid":10608,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T19:39:59.000Z","msg":"1億？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n撩牙都唔夠佢用"},{"pid":"f6f483c2130641cf16decd8fa4852768e4567a6e","tid":406610,"uid":138613,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T20:29:17.000Z","msg":"都要佢肯先得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你一味係度興奮幻想哂佢肯之後會點點點<br />\n做乜啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"